     "\[LineSeparator]returns the equivalent result as ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      RowBox[{
       TemplateBox[{
         Cell[
          TextData["Dot"]], "paclet:ref/Dot"},
        "RefLink",
        BaseStyle->{"InlineFormula"}], "[", 
